<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>팀 랭킹 - 2025 말씀교회 여름수련회</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .navbar-brand { font-weight: bold; }
        .balance-badge { font-size: 1.1em; }
        .ranking-card { transition: transform 0.2s; }
        .ranking-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .gold { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #FFD700, #FFA500); }
        .silver { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #C0C0C0, #A0A0A0); }
        .bronze { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #CD7F32, #B8860B); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <%- include('../partials/navbar', { user: user }) %>

    <main class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                    <h2>팀 랭킹 대시보드</h2>
                    <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn btn-outline-primary">대시보드로 돌아가기</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <h5>점수 계산법</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>기부 점수 = (총 기부금액 ÷ 총 획득금액) × 100</strong></p>
                    <small>팀들은 자신이 획득한 금액 대비 다른 팀에게 기부한 관대함으로 순위가 매겨집니다.</small>
                </div>
                
                <div class="row">
                    <% rankings.forEach((team, index) => { %>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="card ranking-card h-100 <%= index === 0 ? 'gold text-white' : index === 1 ? 'silver' : index === 2 ? 'bronze text-white' : '' %>">
                                <div class="card-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                                        <%= index + 1 %>. <%= team.team_name %>
                                        <% if (index === 0) { %>
                                            🥇
                                        <% } else if (index === 1) { %>
                                            🥈
                                        <% } else if (index === 2) { %>
                                            🥉
                                        <% } %>
                                    </h5>
                                    <span class="badge bg-dark fs-5"><%= team.donation_score %>%</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="row text-center">
                                        <div class="col-6">
                                            <div class="mb-2">
                                                <h6 class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">총 획득금액</h6>
                                                <h5>$<%= team.total_earned %></h5>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6">
                                            <div class="mb-2">
                                                <h6 class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">총 기부금액</h6>
                                                <h5 class="text-success">$<%= team.total_donated %></h5>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <hr class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'border-light' : '' %>">
                                    
                                    <div class="row text-center">
                                        <div class="col-4">
                                            <small class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">인원수</small>
                                            <div><strong><%= team.member_count %></strong></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-4">
                                            <small class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">지출액</small>
                                            <div><strong>$<%= team.total_spent %></strong></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-4">
                                            <small class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">잔액</small>
                                            <div><strong>$<%= team.current_balance %></strong></div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <% if (team.total_earned > 0) { %>
                                        <div class="mt-3">
                                            <div class="progress" style="height: 8px;">
                                                <div class="progress-bar bg-success" 
                                                     role="progressbar" 
                                                     style="width: <%= Math.min(team.donation_score, 100) %>%"
                                                     aria-valuenow="<%= team.donation_score %>" 
                                                     aria-valuemin="0" 
                                                     aria-valuemax="100">
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <small class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">
                                                관대함: 수입의 <%= team.donation_score %>%를 기부함
                                            </small>
                                        </div>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <div class="mt-3">
                                            <small class="<%= index <= 2 ? 'text-light' : 'text-muted' %>">아직 수입 없음</small>
                                        </div>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card mt-4">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">상세 통계</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-striped">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>순위</th>
                                        <th>팀</th>
                                        <th>점수</th>
                                        <th>인원수</th>
                                        <th>획득금액</th>
                                        <th>지출액</th>
                                        <th>기부금액</th>
                                        <th>잔액</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <% rankings.forEach((team, index) => { %>
                                        <tr class="<%= index < 3 ? 'table-warning' : '' %>">
                                            <td>
                                                <strong><%= index + 1 %></strong>
                                                <% if (index === 0) { %>🥇<% } else if (index === 1) { %>🥈<% } else if (index === 2) { %>🥉<% } %>
                                            </td>
                                            <td><strong><%= team.team_name %></strong></td>
                                            <td><span class="badge bg-primary"><%= team.donation_score %>%</span></td>
                                            <td><%= team.member_count %></td>
                                            <td class="text-success">$<%= team.total_earned %></td>
                                            <td class="text-danger">$<%= team.total_spent %></td>
                                            <td class="text-info">$<%= team.total_donated %></td>
                                            <td class="text-primary">$<%= team.current_balance %></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    <% }); %>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        async function logout() {
            try {
                const response = await fetch('/auth/logout', { method: 'POST' });
                if (response.ok) {
                    window.location.href = '/login';
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Logout error:', error);
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>